# Initialize App
## Inital Install, Required once
```npm install```

## Update App Modules
```npm update```


---------------------------------
# Angular2
## Angular2 Startup
```npm start```


## Angular2 Build
To Compile everything into dist/ for distro
```npm run build```


---------------------------------
# Ionic2
## Ionic2 Startup
```npm run ionic-serve```

### Ionic2 switches
--release
Sets debugging to false

--host localhost:3080
Sets Madame Server / Socket Host


## Ionic2 Build
Compiles everything into www/
```npm run ionic-build```

*ionic-build has same Switches as ionic-serve


---------------------------------
### Node Server Startup
* Copy backend/sample.env to backend/.env and fixup any environment variables
```cd backend && node server.js```

